data.description: Welcome to this stunning property that offers an impressive 1855 SqFt of living area, complete with a 2-car garage and situated on a large, inviting corner lot. This home is ready to embrace its new owners with open arms. Step inside and be captivated by the open floor plan that seamlessly connects a generously sized kitchen, a comfortable living room, and a versatile formal dining room or family room. Additionally, the kitchen has a spacious eat-in area, providing flexibility for how you wish to utilize the formal dining or family room space to suit your imagination and lifestyle. The home design continues as sliding doors lead you to a delightful 10x30 screened lanai, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or entertain guests. You'll be pleased to find numerous upgrades throughout the home, including beautiful leaded glass on the front door, upgraded lighting fixtures and ceiling fans, a spacious attic with flooring and lights, with a convenient pull-down ladder for easy access. The kitchen sink and faucet have been tastefully upgraded, and an in-wall pest control system ensures your home stays comfortable and pest-free. AC was replaced April 2023. Conveniently located in the tranquil Mable Loop Ridge Subdivision, this property is just minutes away from Hwy 27, providing easy access to nearby amenities, schools, and more. Notably, this area qualifies for USDA eligibility, making it even more enticing for potential buyers. Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your own. Schedule an appointment today to view this gem and envision the endless possibilities it offers.
